headline: Public Storage: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The real estate investment trust, based in Glendale, California, said it had funds from operations of $758.7 million, or $4.31 per share, in the period. The average estimate of eight analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $4.24 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
